rust/0000018b-57f8-d8e2-a1eb-f7fe8cb50000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯扣押的人质：从以色列被绑架的人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-22/ty-article-magazine/hostages-held-by-hamas-the-names-of-those-abducted-from-israel/0000018b-55f8-d5d2-afef-d5fdd04e0000</link><description>10 月 7 日，超过 200 人——以色列人和非以色列人、婴儿、妇女和老人、平民和士兵——被哈马斯恐怖分子俘虏，并被武力带到加沙。以下是所有经官方确认的人质姓名</description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Oct 2023 16:41:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-22/ty-article-magazine/hostages-held-by-hamas-the-names-of-those-abducted-from-israel/0000018b-55f8-d5d2-afef-d5fdd04e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列对加沙长达16年的封锁失败了。这真的是唯一的选择吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-22/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israels-16-year-blockade-of-gaza-failed-was-it-really-the-only-option/0000018b-57f3-d2b2-addf-77fb07f60000</link><description>许多以色列分析人士一致认为，封锁加沙是对付哈马斯的唯一途径。但 10 月 7 日的灾难性袭击引发了严峻的问题：封锁政策是否是以色列的另一个重要战略误解</description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Oct 2023 16:40:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-22/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israels-16-year-blockade-of-gaza-failed-was-it-really-the-only-option/0000018b-57f3-d2b2-addf-77fb07f60000</guid></item><item><title>“携带枪支，这是救星：本格维尔和他的妻子吹嘘以色列携带武器的人数急剧增加</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-22/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-and-his-wife-boast-of-arming-jewish-israelis/0000018b-5753-d473-a5fb-77db1c2d0000</link><description>上周，以色列议会国家安全委员会批准了国家安全部长本-格维尔提出的枪支许可证规定修正案，以便在南部战事持续不断的情况下，获得许可证的条件更加宽松</description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Oct 2023 15:41:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-22/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-and-his-wife-boast-of-arming-jewish-israelis/0000018b-5753-d473-a5fb-77db1c2d0000</guid></item><item><title>150,000 枚火箭和导弹：以色列在与真主党的战争中将遭遇的武器</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-10-22/ty-article-magazine/.premium/150-000-rockets-and-missiles-the-weapons-israel-would-encounter-in-a-war-with-hezbollah/0000018b-573d-d2b2-addf-777df6210000</link><description>根据最新的已知评估，真主党拥有数万枚可深入以色列境内的远程导弹、广泛的防空系统和突击队</description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Oct 2023 15:33:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-10-22/ty-article-magazine/.premium/150-000-rockets-and-missiles-the-weapons-israel-would-encounter-in-a-war-with-hezbollah/0000018b-573d-d2b2-addf-777df6210000</guid></item><item><title>美国高级官员警告以色列-加沙战争中中东局势升级的可能性增加</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2023-10-22/ty-article/.premium/senior-u-s-officials-warn-about-increasing-escalation-amid-israel-gaza-war/0000018b-57af-d473-a5fb-77ef7d5b0000</link><description>美国国防部长劳埃德·奥斯汀和国务卿安东尼·布林肯认为“局势可能会大幅升级”，担心真主党和伊朗可能与以色列发生直接冲突</description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Oct 2023 14:54:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2023-10-22/ty-article/.premium/senior-u-s-officials-warn-about-increasing-escalation-amid-israel-gaza-war/0000018b-57af-d473-a5fb-77ef7d5b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列与哈马斯战争的斗争正在华盛顿升温</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-22/ty-article/.premium/the-battle-over-the-israel-hamas-war-is-heating-up-in-washington/0000018b-5735-d2b2-addf-777d25eb0000</link><description>尽管美国总统乔·拜登表示他全力支持以色列，但其官员的行动却描绘出一幅略有不同的景象。华盛顿特区的民主党和共和党内部也出现了第二条战线</description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Oct 2023 14:40:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-22/ty-article/.premium/the-battle-over-the-israel-hamas-war-is-heating-up-in-washington/0000018b-5735-d2b2-addf-777d25eb0000</guid></item></channel></rss>